org.jetel.graph.runtime.tracker

Class ComplexComponentTokenTracker

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.jetel.graph.runtime.tracker.BasicComponentTokenTracker
      • org.jetel.graph.runtime.tracker.ComplexComponentTokenTracker
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ComponentTokenTracker
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    ReformatComponentTokenTracker

    public class ComplexComponentTokenTracker
extends BasicComponentTokenTracker
    This token tracker is used in components by default. Suitable for components creating N out-tokens for one in-token. All received tokens are freed. All written tokens are linked to the last read token.
